HEADWORD: Snet
<hw>Snet</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Snot</er>.]</ety> <def>The
clear of mucus; to blow.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Snetting</xex> his nose.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Holland.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

